exercise

Weight = float(input("Weight? "))
kilobilo = input(("Kilo or Pound? "))

if kilobilo == "K" or kilobilo == "k":
    print(Weight * 0.453592)
elif kilobilo == "L" or kilobilo == "l":
    print(Weight)
